		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You might be thinking of nsfcoll.zip that was compiled by kevtris.  I believe he did take the sound effects out.  It's still on the site here: <a href="http://nesdev.com/nsfcoll.zip" class="postlink">http://nesdev.com/nsfcoll.zip</a>, from 17 years ago.  Lots of NSFs had not been ripped by that point in time though.

		

