	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, there are actually a number of people who are unhappy that many original NSFs were ripped without their sound effects, and are reripping /arranging them to include the SFX.  &quot;SFX are an integral part of the game experience / sound code; let's preserve them too&quot; sort of argument.<br /><br />Yes SFX / No SFX will probably never reach a consensus, I think.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


